    <item>
      <title>Hello, World</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/my-first-post/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/my-first-post/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Welcome. After thinking about it for way too long, I&amp;rsquo;ve finally decided to start writing publicly about things I find interesting.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;why-start-a-blog&#34; class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Why Start a Blog? &lt;span class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34; style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#why-start-a-blog&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ve always found that writing helps me think more clearly. Whether I&amp;rsquo;m learning something new, building a project, or just trying to work through an idea, putting words on a page forces me to organize my thoughts.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>About</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/about/</link>
